sentences.english: Researchers have found a large subpopulation of the insect that prefers to live outside.
sentences.chinese: 研究人員發現了一種喜歡生活在室外的瘧蚊的亞種。

sentences.english: Carried by the female anopheles mosquito, malaria is a disease of the poor.
sentences.chinese: 瘧疾由雌性瘧蚊傳播，是窮人的疾病。

sentences.english: A report about the malaria mosquito sweet bait was published in Malaria Journal.
sentences.chinese: 關於瘧蚊甜味誘餌的報告發表在《瘧疾雜誌》上。
